org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.common.tuples

Class TripleWithCandidates<K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple
      • org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple4<K,K,K,boolean[]>
        • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.common.tuples.TripleWithCandidates<K>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - key type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class TripleWithCandidates<K>
extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple4<K,K,K,boolean[]>
    Represents an edge, source and target vertex triple that matches at least one triple in the data graph. Each triple contains a list of identifiers that match to edge ids in the query graph. f0: edge id f1: source vertex id f2: target vertex id f3: edge query candidates
